  "articleContent": "<div>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\">Outside the window, the late snow blows through an early spring. In that quiet stretch of waiting, the girl slips into a gentle dream.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">In dreams, she finds a distant starry sky, warmth in her hands, and the one she has been waiting for, there as promised.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">Mornye's Deluxe Outfit <span style=\"color: rgb(195, 158, 85);\"><strong>\"Plush Dream\"</strong> </span>will become available once Version 3.3 goes live. Get a sneak peek now!<br><br>\n<div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"0\" data-line=\"true\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 158, 85);\">✦How to Obtain✦</span></strong></div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\">Mornye's Deluxe Outfit <span style=\"color: rgb(195, 158, 85);\"><strong>\"Plush Dream\"</strong></span> will be made permanently available in the Store once Version 3.3 goes live.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">Purchase the Outfit during Version 3.3 at a discount, for 1980 Lunites only. After Version 3.3 ends, the Outfit costs 2480 Lunites.</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"2\" data-line=\"true\">&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/fbc7wtwkpayxcw9ks5-1776771284800.jpeg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/fx7copoi0xf3b9siry-1776771378349.jpeg\" width=\"1080\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/jr3kummed9iriql44d-1776771419765.gif\" width=\"1080\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/10cpewsmqtl5pa596d-1776771447745.gif\" width=\"1080\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/qs3co1utqcs1gir1l5-1776771466485.gif\" width=\"1080\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/akiwebsite/website2.0/images/1776700800000/38yj6xg4tgyahrx6xh-1776771483580.jpeg\" width=\"1080\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\"><br><br></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
